data.description: Welcome to 2106 Chippendale!  This meticulously maintained home is nestled on a quiet street in the heart of booming Oak Forest.   The home features an all brick exterior, sprinkler system, and energy efficient windows. The living room is bright and spacious with space for a formal dining room.  The classic kitchen has been upgraded with new granite countertops and stainless steel appliances and includes a large eat-in breakfast area. Both the primary and secondary bathroom have new countertops, toilets and tile throughout.  In the back you will find a large, covered patio, and tasteful landscaping.  The 20x24 detached building already has electricity and can be used as a workshop, gym, man cave... the options are endless.  The house has never flooded and no burst pipes during either recent big freeze.   Easy access to all major highways, shopping centers and restaurants.  Within minutes to WhiteOak Bayou Trail and TJ Jester pool/park.
